Title: Just for the Summer (Part of Your World, #3)
Author: Abby Jimenez
My Review: This book was a five-star read for me! I absolutely loved every second of it, especially the two main characters. I’ve never rooted for a couple as much as I did for Emma and Justin. Their journey through trauma and hardship was captivating which made their connection even more special in the end. Even the supporting characters were well-written and fit into the overall story well.
